On Remote Server:
1. Install Python
2. Open page: http://{hostname}:15672/cli/rabbitmqadmin
3. Download and Set Path of rabbitmqadmin in envt variables
4. Check rabbitmqadmin by typing:
python.exe rabbitmqadmin --help
5. Now see all queues:
python.exe rabbitmqadmin list queues name
6. To delete a single queue:
python.exe rabbitmqadmin delete queue name='queuename'
7. To delete all queues:(Using Policy)
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11459676/delete-all-the-queues-from-rabbitmq
8. To purge a queue:
python.exe rabbitmqadmin purge queue name=name_of_queue